  "description": "<p>MEC down sleeping bags have been popular for decades and are known for prices that are waaay cheaper than comparable options. The Draco line uses high-end down and tightly woven Pertex nylon that sheds moisture and prevents the down from working its way out. Vertical baffles over the chest keep the down in place, so you won't discover a cold spot as you shift around during the night.</p><ul><li>Pertex Quantum ripstop nylon shell has a DWR treatment to shed moisture and a tight weave to retain down</li><li>30-denier woven nylon lining</li><li>Insulated with 650 fill power duck down that meets the Responsible Down Standard for animal welfare</li><li>Vertical baffles over the torso prevents cold spots</li><li>Wide cut gives you room to sprawl, but still provides thermal efficiency</li><li>Hood and shoulder drawcords have different profiles, so you can tell them apart in the dark</li><li>YKK #8 zip connects to most other MEC bags</li><li>Neck yoke and draft tube keep heat in and cold out</li><li>Small internal pocket holds contact lenses or headlamp</li><li>Draw cord stuff sack and large storage sack included</li><li>EN standard tested, for dependable temperature ratings</li></ul>",
